hopobject.body: Canada>Canada lowe aurora plus Unlike most states, Michigans constitution protects the rights of people who work for a governmental entity (e.g. the City of Detroit) to not have their pensions or retirement systems diminished, Dubin said in an e-mail. I applaud the attorney generals intended legal action to protect the citizens of our state who rely on their constitutional protections guaranteed by the State of Michigan.
